ğŸ“Œ Project Overview

The Menu Driven Billing Calculator is a simple Python-based project that allows users to perform basic billing and arithmetic operations through a menu-driven interface. This project is ideal for beginners to understand core Python concepts in a practical way.

ğŸ¯ Problem Statement

To design and implement a menu-driven billing calculator that enables users to perform basic arithmetic operations such as addition, subtraction, multiplication, division, viewing the total bill amount, and exiting the program.

